description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Fox Sports Bruce Feldman about last night's Ohio State Game and previews this weekend's slate. Former NFL Safety Rodney joins us to talk Patriots and makes some predictions. And Hall of Fame John Oates of Hall & Oates to sing with Fritzy.
